node.text:
LINK IN MY BIO for the sticker/magnet… but there’s more: You guys ever watch Willy Wonka and The Chocolate Factory? Well I kinda stole that golden ticket idea. 
Here’s the shtick:

-If you buy a sticker or a magnet, you have a chance to ALSO receive a silver or golden ticket (I made only 1 of each).

-No, you won’t be gifted ownership of this Insta page 😅, but you do get something else…

-Silver Ticket: you get 1 free uncolored commission! I’ll draw whatever you want (within reason), and send you the JPEG file or physical paper.

-Golden Ticket: you get one free FULLY-colored commission ooooor I’ll incorporate you as a character in a future P and B comic!

-Each ticket has instructions on the back on how to claim your prize, GOOD LUCK!

-Well… I guess it makes no sense for me to wish you ALL good luck, right? I mean, even if wishing good luck onto someone had any sort of cosmic odds-influencing power, me wishing it onto ALL of you offers nobody an advantage. It all balances out, so I might as well not have wished everyone luck in the first place, you know? Aw well, GOOD LUCK!
.
.
.
#relatable #sliceoflife #funny #meme #funnymeme #comicartist #illustration #shortcomic #pixieandbrutus #webtoon #graphicnovel #dogsandcats #kitten #puppy
